     <h1>澳门荷官亲身讲诉，高薪背后的日与夜</h1> 
     <div class="xgxx">
      <a href="/author/Lovedp1037macau.html">Love澳门</a> 2017-03-14
     </div> 
     <div class="zw"> 
      <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="__bg_gif" src="http://pics.haik8.com/nqvaoZtoY6GlxJuvYKfWmZlkxaJhpc-bna9ieYyFfI/yZgJdnxX-En6qzc3l7oq97nZ2winidyqqlhaSZlKhmqICM3XyWkaier9B9iHR-l5F_l892nq_ImpafeJFjcIKQq3m-n5V_iKODmnuDlabfhKOHkWRxr9qYmqKnbZmhmQ.jpg" style="line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;" width="auto" /></p>
      <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">调戏小编，加私人微信：macau587</strong></span></strong></p>
      <p><br /></p>
      <p><br /></p>
      <p><span style="font-size: 14px;">大家都以为澳门人十分幸福，很多人都可以到赌场当荷官，领着高薪，令人羡慕不已！其实你不知道，澳门荷官背后的辛酸！</span></p>
      <p><br /></p>
      <p><iframe allowfullscreen="" class="video_iframe" src="https://v.qq.com/iframe/preview.html?vid=p0383c4afxq&amp;width=500&amp;height=375&amp;auto=0" data-vidtype="1" frameborder="0" height="252" scrolling="no" width="336"></iframe></p>
      <p style="text-align: right;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);">视频来自：澳亚卫视</span></p>
      <p><br /></p>
      <p><br /></p>
      <p style="text-align: center;">------------ &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="font-size: 14px;">华丽的分割线（内容延伸）</span><span style="line-height: 25.6000003814697px;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="line-height: 25.6000003814697px; text-align: center;"></span><span style="line-height: 25.6000003814697px; text-align: center;">------------</span></span></p>
      <p><br /></p>
      <p><br /></p>
      <section class="" label="powered by 135editor.com" style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
       <section class="" data-color="rgb(33, 33, 34)" data-custom="rgb(33, 33, 34)" data-id="2873" style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-top-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-color: initial; word-wrap: break-word !important; ">
        <section style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(33, 33, 34); word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(33, 33, 34);">
         <section style="padding: 16px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(33, 33, 34); word-wrap: break-word !important; background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(135deg, transparent, transparent 4px, rgb(255, 255, 255) 4px, rgb(255, 255, 255) 12px);">
          <section class="" data-style="font-size:16px;weight:bold" style="padding: 8px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 33, 34); border-color: rgb(33, 33, 34); word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);">
           <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">烟雾缭绕的吸烟室内，一个消瘦的年轻人看到记者进来，轻声说：“兄弟，给支烟抽...”</span></p>
           <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
           <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
           <section style="max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
            <span style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">点着后，他问记者“战绩如何？”</span>
           </section>
           <section style="max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
            <br class="" style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;" />
           </section>
           <section style="max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
            <span style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">我告诉他“就来看看，没下池。”</span>
           </section>
           <section style="max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
            <br class="" style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;" />
           </section>
           <section style="max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
            <span style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">他并没在意，苍白的脸微仰，无神地盯着天花板：“输了四万了。回香港的船票都没了...”</span>
           </section>
           <section style="max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
            <br class="" style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;" />
           </section>
           <section style="max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
            <span style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">这时，吸烟室的门打开，又进来一名老者，两人似乎相识，寒暄之后，便走到房间一角，开始“分析得失”。</span>
           </section>
           <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
          </section>
         </section>
        </section>
        <section style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section>
       </section>
       <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
      </section>
      <p><br /></p>
      <section style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
       <section class="" label="powered by 135editor.com" style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
        <p style="margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">在澳门众多娱乐场里，这样的情形每天都在上演。而与得意或失意的赌客相映的，则是每张赌台后边身着礼服的发牌员，又称“庄荷” (Dealer，或Croupier)，是指在赌场内负责发牌、杀（收回客人输掉筹码）赔（赔彩）的工作者。不管台面上多么风云变幻，他们永远笑容可掬，用极少的言语和熟练的手势“决定”着顾客荷包的大小，因此还被称为“荷官”。</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-s="300,640" src="http://pics.haik8.com/nqvaoZtoY6GlxJuvYKfWmZlkxaJhpc-bna9ieYyFfI/yZgJdnxYCobICzoqlimL6hanqwlnh6r3trnpVzrK99sKGMupmlo6iXocRpZWN6p2ern8Oga5K7qWd3nJGBhoipn5i1fNWHfXl53Jh5lZDLfIOBuKR2iZFvaGVyp6qXmaSqdNChxqA.jpg" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <section class="" style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
         <section class="" style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-top-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-color: initial; word-wrap: break-word !important; ">
          <section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
           <section style="margin: 5px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 8px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; height: 25px; float: left; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122);"></section>
           <section style="padding: 5px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
            <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">入职考心算，月薪近2万</span></p>
           </section>
          </section>
         </section>
        </section>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">阿君入行做荷官已经7年，每天工作八小时，每个星期工作六天，每月能够拿到约14000人民币的薪水，如遇生病，“澳门政府每年会给市民六天病假。”</span><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">阿君说，每天的工作看似轻松，实际上需要精神高度集中，每个荷官在每张台工作大概两小时左右就会更换，然而即使这样，也难免不会出现差错，“主要靠保持精神吧！如果出错会按照情况来定，一般是给一个警告，三个警告就会给一个严重警告，受到两个严重警告就会被解雇！不过出错一年后不再犯就会取消。”</p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">入职做荷官并不难，阿君透露，理论上年满21岁的澳门居民都可以，同普通公司应聘一样，主要分为笔试和面试，“笔试主要考加减乘除的心算。”</p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-s="300,640" src="http://pics.haik8.com/nqvaoZtoY6GlxJuvYKfWmZlkxaJhpc-bna9ieYyFfI/yZgJdnxYCobICzoqlimL6hanqwlnh6r3trnpVza4-Fem1wlpKys4OnmcarrJuZrpmZbMZmZ4PLnI5qonGbmqeOaXmcmaJpnZWc2JuWmaubmZefw6mkbLmGiJxiZmZocq6ulsye1XaepJ3J.jpg" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">荷官的上升通道也相对比较清晰，大致分为普通荷官、监场主任、经理。薪水也会随着职务的提升而提升，已在澳门某娱乐场做到监场主任的陈姐入行已8年，做普通荷官2年，第3年开始做监场主任至今。陈姐透露，一般的监场主任月薪19000元人民币，而最低层级的副经理薪资则为22000元。（备注：以上薪水为2015年采访时得知的薪水，仅供参考。）</p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">Joyce在赌场任职已有11年，其中三年是荷官，四年是监场主任，现在已经升任监场经理（Pit Manager），主要负责处理日常事务，监管荷官、主任在赌台事务运作，并协助上司尽快处理小问题，如客人纠纷，下属问题，安排人手等等。</p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">Joyce并不认为经理的职位有多么特殊：“赌场职级有很多层，所以我的职级真的很普通。经理与主任最大分别是，经理已经算是管理层了，而主任只负责监督荷官在赌台的正常运作，相比之下，经理负责杂项较多。”</p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-s="300,640" src="http://pics.haik8.com/nqvaoZtoY6GlxJuvYKfWmZlkxaJhpc-bna9ieYyFfI/yZgJdnxYCobICzoqlimL6hanqwlnh6r3trnpVzdJGmn62gyZvNaYaaasOLr4Vrn4lrariFdaHDsIZonXF1cZSjrHvTnKSrfZqg3Gp_a6PPkpCB2m2pZ5htZHSqqJGeoKtzodaWyA.jpg" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <section class="" style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
         <section class="" style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-top-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-color: initial; word-wrap: break-word !important; ">
          <section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
           <section style="margin: 5px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 8px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; height: 25px; float: left; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122);"></section>
           <section style="padding: 5px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
            <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">荷官们最不喜欢香港赌客</span></p>
           </section>
          </section>
         </section>
        </section>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">相应的，随着职务的提升，工作内容也会不同。“每天上班由特定部门编排去哪个区或哪个贵宾厅，由经理安排负责2-3张赌桌，监督荷官的工作流程，每2小时负责结算此赌桌输赢数并提出报告，同时也会处理一些突发的事件。”陈姐所说的“突发事件”很多是输了钱赌客闹事，成千上万乃至数十万的筹码瞬间消失，一些赌客难免情绪失控，而对于这种情况，赌场也会有自己的一套处理方式。</span><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">“很多赌客会得到一些优惠券，尽量大事化小，小事化了，外资公司比较兴这套。” 陈姐的说法也得到了阿君的印证，作为荷官经常会遇到一些“没有赌品”的客人，“他们会发脾气，对我们说粗话甚至扔牌！”</p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-s="300,640" src="http://pics.haik8.com/nqvaoZtoY6GlxJuvYKfWmZlkxaJhpc-bna9ieYyFfI/yZgJdnxYCobICzoqlimL6hanqwlnh6r3trnpVza39oiKycmKqVm4iBqJWVoqWIz5GLbKWdlYTcg66jqKqifGqLjHidnaijmHiixqF-qJnOc4CusKthbpZpc6yrj5ilp3Sgp8uY.jpg" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">在赌场工作多了，荷官们也练就了一双认客的“火眼金睛”，客人来自哪个地方一眼便知。</p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">“有钱人脾气大部分都很好，其实最不受荷官欢迎的不是内地人，而是香港人！出了名又小气又斤斤计较！</p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">阿君情绪激动地说，出了纠纷，大部分赌客都会大事化小，只有香港人小事化大。”</p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">然而以为闹事就会得到好处，就全错了，陈姐告诉记者：“还有一些公司很少这么做，如果遇到不讲理又想闹事的赌客，会被外佣保安绑进保安室打。赌场绝不会容许赌客耍横。”</p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">不过Joyce表示这种状况在以前才有，“旧时只有葡京独大，可能会这样处理问题，而现在外资公司管理下，很少这种黑色地带。赌场也是服务顾客嘛。”</p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-s="300,640" src="http://pics.haik8.com/nqvaoZtoY6GlxJuvYKfWmZlkxaJhpc-bna9ieYyFfI/yZgJdnxYCobICzoqlimL6hanqwlnh6r3trnpVzdJGmn62gyZvNaYaaasOLr4Vrn4lrariFdaHDsIZonXF1cZSjrHvTnKSrfZqg3Gp_a6PPkpCB2m2pZ5htZHSqqJGeoKtzodaWyA.jpg" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <section class="" style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
         <section class="" style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-top-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-color: initial; word-wrap: break-word !important; ">
          <section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
           <section style="margin: 5px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 8px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; height: 25px; float: left; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122);"></section>
           <section style="padding: 5px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
            <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">千万富翁变赤贫，荷官感悟良多</span></p>
           </section>
          </section>
         </section>
        </section>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">作为荷官，在工作之余也可以变成赌客，“只不过不允许在自己任职的赌场赌。”阿君认为，即使荷官，去赌博的话也不会赢面更大，“赌博主要是靠运气，没什么技术可以依靠。”因此，阿君也从不去其他赌场，“我见过一千万只用两小时就输得一干二净。”</span><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">“赌博，赢钱只是瞬间，长赌必输。”在娱乐场中浸淫多年，见得多了，陈姐显然很有感悟：“有个街坊，十几年前是千万富翁，当时澳门的房子几十万/套，而现在近千万/套，可见在当时，千万富翁是真的有钱！结果这名街坊不幸染上赌瘾，前两天，我在观光塔附近见他满脸胡须，开着工地车送泥沙。”</p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">“还有内地富豪的儿子带着女朋友，过年时在我们公司输了几百万，还因为逾期逗留2个多月，按每日每人500元的标准被罚款。”</p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-s="300,640" src="http://pics.haik8.com/nqvaoZtoY6GlxJuvYKfWmZlkxaJhpc-bna9ieYyFfI/yZgJdnxYCobICzoqlimL6hanqwlnh6r3trnpVzdp6WoJholn_ObWeOjLmDp2No0GWqh7qXe6zVkaR8mZyjj6l6n5rYhc-me3WC2KSCiamtpId8lKthbpZpc6yrj5ilp3Sgp8uY.jpg" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">从概率学角度来讲，一般来说，根据赌场游戏的规则制定，赌场总会占有一定的优势，获胜的概率会向赌场倾斜，这叫做“赌场优势”。</p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">另外，赌场的盈利方式还有“抽水”（即佣金），用一句流传已久的话就是：“靠开赌场赚钱，而不是靠赌钱赚钱。”</p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">而遇到运气好的客人，赌场会不会任由客人赢钱呢？显然也不会，陈姐告诉记者，“客人不断赢钱，闭路电视会跟紧，首先观察流程是否正确。如果流程正确，庄荷正确杀赔，我们公司就由客人赢钱，不过最后要写份报告给上司；但如果这种情况发生在私人老板的贵宾厅，就会换庄荷。”</p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">由于涉及钱财，荷官和出纳人员在操作过程中有很多细节要注意，比如最常见的：不能“手交手”，即现金及筹码放在桌面上，客人离手了再拿，陈姐透露：“这是怕工作人员与客人连手，放在桌面上，扬手给闭路电视看，再由客人取走。”</p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">“只要是规范的赢钱，赌场也是没有办法。做赌场的，客人肯定要有输有赢，每个赌客都天天输钱，谁还来呀？”不过，陈姐也表示，普通游客几千几万的输赢，其实对赌场毫无影响，赌场真正的赚钱来源是贵宾厅，“贵宾厅不设门坎，只是最低投注起i比较高，普通大厅有300、500、1000等不同起点，而贵宾厅最低每局3000，贵宾厅的包房最低桌面100万，每局最低投注1万。有大客，又输了大钱，当日利润肯定高，主要靠贵宾厅的杀数。”</p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-s="300,640" src="http://pics.haik8.com/nqvaoZtoY6GlxJuvYKfWmZlkxaJhpc-bna9ieYyFfI/yZgJdnxYCobICzoqlimL6hanqwlnh6r3trnpVzd5mjpJ-atKPCm66jgqegjXqazYqgrrh1lYrLnHlrdHWdqIh-pIHYeZlpgHePk5qYm5jIk5-Zznmqr5FvaGVyp6qXmaSqdNChxqA.jpg" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <section class="" style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
         <section class="" style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-top-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-color: initial; word-wrap: break-word !important; ">
          <section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
           <section style="margin: 5px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 8px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; height: 25px; float: left; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122);"></section>
           <section style="padding: 5px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
            <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">奇特的“博彩专业”学士学位</span></p>
           </section>
          </section>
         </section>
        </section>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">不过，赌场的辉煌已经渐现疲态，据报道，澳门博彩业今年4月份收入水平同比再度下降38.8%，与各界预期的下降39%基本持平，原因在于中国内地的反腐和A股市场的牛市，这些都阻止了更多投机资金流向澳门赌场。摩根士丹利指出，澳门的赌场座席和酒店客房数量预计会在未来18个月内增加50%，这对于整个行业而言都是灾难性的。该机构因而指出，澳门博彩业市场在短期内没有触底回升的可能性。</span><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">虽然赌场遭遇“寒冬”，但由于自身休闲旅游中心的定位，博彩业对相关人才仍有需求。作为澳门本地的一所实用型高校，澳门理工学院共有19个学士学位专业，其中一项就是“博彩专业”。在参访期间，学校的老师告诉记者，博彩专业在这里被划归于管理类，博彩专业毕业生更多进入博彩业的管理工作岗位，“据我所知，澳门似乎只有我们在提供博彩专业管理的课程。为澳门建立国际休闲旅游文化中心提供人才储备。”</p>
        <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       </section>
       <section style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
        <span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span>
       </section>
       <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-s="300,640" src="http://pics.haik8.com/nqvaoZtoY6GlxJuvYKfWmZlkxaJhpc-bna9ieYyFfI/yZgJdnxYCobICzoqlimL6hanqwlnh6r3trnpVzmI6BpW6ZtJ-WcKeabbeafWdr2Xd_aparm5vYgGeIaHdma5-HkKmXfZaqa52ZyXptaabOe6KfxZ2TiZFvaGVyp6qXmaSqdNChxqA.jpg" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
